
   Compile from the main 'src' directory with:

      make -f ./makefiles/[MAKEFILE] [OPTION]

   [MAKEFILE] is one of the files listed below.

      Makefile.ifort_intelmpi : intel fortran compiler with intel mpi
      Makefile.ifort_openmpi  : intel fortran compiler with openmpi

   [OPTION] is one of the option listed below.

      help      : print this help
      config    : pre-compilation of libraries
      opt       : structure optimizer
      gen       : coordinate generator
      test      : test program
      all       : 'config' then 'opt' and 'gen'
      clean     : clean 'src' directory
      veryclean : clean 'src' and libraries in subdirectories

